The paper discusses the logical aspects of quantum theory, including logics for specification and analysis of quantum information systems. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.PL (Programming Languages). Additionally, the paper specifically mentions quantum theory, indicating that it could also belong to the quant-ph (Quantum Physics) sub-category.
